日志
=======
@see ["logging: logstash and other things" by Jordan Sissel, czar of ](http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RuUFnog29M4&list=PLynE-g6Vl6LFxT0SM7g1hkGqkHLTpca7x)

格式
---------------
    （timestamp）（事件的描述/用来描述此事件的数据存储）
    TimeStamp + DATA = LOG !

    ##相关工具：
    > transport : flume ,fluentd ,scribe ,rsyslog,syslog-ng;
    > search + analytics: hadoop, graylog2,elsa
    >  storage: hdfs , cassandra ,elasticsearch

    logstash
    GROK